title: MS Windows 7 Ultimate SP1 32-bit English integrated March 2014
description:
Windows 7 Ultimate SP1 x86 English only, Integrated March 2014
--------------------------------------------------------------


Source for this release was an original Microsoft Windows 7 Ultimate SP1 32-bit English ISO. 

Integrated Microsoft updates until 15.03.2014 incl. Internet Explorer 11.

- It's an original image from Microsoft except for the added updates and IE11.
- This version is NOT cracked or activated nor otherwise tampered with.
- This release is 100% clean!
- Only updates from Microsoft were used.
- Feel free to scan for viruses.

I made this DVD for professional use at work.
You may use a original product key from MS

The only program used is WinToolkit1433, which is needed to integrate .net4.5.1 and other POST installation updates.

A lot of work has gone into this and I do hope that there are people out there who will appreciate it.

A list of all updates that were used is included.

Enjoy
